---
<Base title="SEO Case Study: Guildford Property Firm Results" description="How a Guildford High Street estate agency approached local pack visibility through local SEO, area guides, and GBP optimisation." schema={schema}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose">
